description: Manage the registration assignments in Azure.

commands.name: az managedservices assignment create
commands.syntax:
az managedservices assignment create --definition
                                     [--assignment-id]
                                     [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                     [--resource-group]

commands.name: az managedservices assignment delete
commands.syntax:
az managedservices assignment delete --assignment
                                     [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                     [--resource-group]
                                     [--yes]

commands.name: az managedservices assignment list
commands.syntax:
az managedservices assignment list [--include-definition {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                   [--max-items]
                                   [--next-token]
                                   [--resource-group]

commands.name: az managedservices assignment show
commands.syntax:
az managedservices assignment show --assignment
                                   [--include-definition {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                   [--resource-group]
examples: az managedservices assignment show --assignment d3087cf0-e180-4cca-b147-54ae00c7b504 --include-definition true

commands.name: az managedservices assignment wait
commands.summary: Place the CLI in a waiting state until a condition is met.
commands.syntax:
az managedservices assignment wait --assignment
                                   --scope
                                   [--created]
                                   [--custom]
                                   [--deleted]
                                   [--exists]
                                   [--include-definition {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                   [--interval]
                                   [--timeout]
                                   [--updated]
